title: Estadio Correcaminos
text:
Estadio Correcaminos is a multi-use stadium in <a href="San%20Francisco%20Gotera%2C%20El%20Salvador">San Francisco Gotera, El Salvador</a>. 
It is currently used mostly for <a href="football%20%28soccer%29">football</a> matches and is the home stadium of <a href="Fuerte%20San%20Francisco">Fuerte San Francisco</a>.
It is named after the team's nickname. The cost of its construction was US$510,000. The stadium holds 12,000 people.
